Now anyway, let's move on to if/else statments:

[#if condition] {expression or block}.

Example:

[#if 4 < 5] ...;

or

[#if 4 < 5] [#block] ... [#/block];

or 

Can keep going...
[#if 4 < 5] [#if condition] [#if condition] ...

Else:

[#if condition] {code}
[#else] {code}

[#if condition] {code}
[#else] [#if condition]

Or easy elseif:

[#if condition] {code}
[#else if condition] {code}

[#if condition] {code}
[#elif condition]

You can also do that same thing where you just keep going.
An if statement is also a block.